{"tid":1045500,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"留低你食過好既steak house","createTime":"2019-03-03T15:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T17:46:58.000Z","uid":240223,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f37af78a0d721b3bf73cd843881ce597eccab190","tid":1045500,"uid":240223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"個人覺得金鐘間Ruth Chris<br />\n環境一流<br />\n牛扒煎完有塊牛油係面俾佢慢慢溶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好大塊。次次都係勉強食得晒<br />\n價錢都要六舊一塊<br />\n個New York cheesecake 係必試<br />\n<br />\n近依2年鐘意去Buenos Aires Polo Club<br />\n服務同牛扒都好好<br />\n價錢俾Ruth Chris 平差唔多一半<br />\n入面既環境裝修 我覺得物超所值<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8377198981502b4000471331c3d33d6d67da521","tid":1045500,"uid":80173,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:42:36.000Z","msg":"la vache！"},{"pid":"ad2e95a957f9249c44f6dd03bfcc4122f554984b","tid":1045500,"uid":171572,"like":1,"dislike":34,"score":-33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"頂級 Outback<br />\n中檔 金鳳<br />\n低檔 大快樂"},{"pid":"2033462a769f0595b5f9542f3656b6bc026af7cc","tid":1045500,"uid":6715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"Porter house"},{"pid":"9d4d59e169dc4ff0eae4b335e8b44be8772315c9","tid":1045500,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"牛扒其實睇Grade<br />\nUSDA Prime Angus 牛小排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇Grade重要過邊間餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ce5ff3ba835e9f67106b248d7b046b43af72ca","tid":1045500,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"花園餐廳"},{"pid":"6cfb3f6f474426cd0921672c10ef91bc3feb140f","tid":1045500,"uid":240223,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ad2e95a957f9249c4